('ESL WORKSHOP: ENLIVENING YOUR ACADEMIC WRITING', 'Workshops', '16.00', '2015-03-10', 'Academic writing doesn’t have to be boring. In this workshop you will learn how to add elements such as metaphor and idiom to your writing to give it more colour.\r\n\r\nCost:\r\nN/A\r\n\r\nContact\r\nFor more information, contact esl@dal.ca, call 94-8062, or visit our website.', 'Mona Campbell Building Room 1110', 41),
