('ENGINEERS NOVA SCOTIA PRESENTS: HOW TO NETWORK AND THE HALIFAX JOB MARKET', 'Training & Professional Development', '17.00 - 19.30', '2015-03-12', 'Join the Young Professionals Group and Halifax Partnership Connector Program Team on March 12th, 2015 at 5PM in Room B310, Dalhousie Engineering Sexton Campus, for a workshop on the Halifax Job Market and How to Network your way to finding an opportunity. This event is targeted at soon-to-graduate students and guests are welcome to attend the session or just the networking event at 6PM. ', 'Dalhousie Engineering, Room B310, 5269 Morris Street, Halifax', 53),
