('HUNGRY GAMES: PRESENTED BY THE DALHOUSIE ARTS AND SOCIAL SCIENCES SOCIETY', 'Special Events', '11.00 - 13.00', '2015-03-14', 'At first, it was a reminder of the rebellion, but I think it’s growing from that. I think it’s something that knits us all together” \r\n\r\nNow the time has come for us to select the courageous for the honour of representing their district in the Dalhousie Arts and Social Sciences Hungry Games. Will you volunteer as tribute? \r\n\r\nSign up for your chance to WIN the Hungry Games from Monday, March 2nd to March 11th in the McCain Lobby. \r\n\r\n$5 per tribute to play with all proceeds going towards Feed Nova Scotia. \r\n\r\nPrizes will be offered to the tributes with: \r\nLast one standing: $300 \r\nMost "hits": $100 \r\nBest costume: $50 \r\n\r\nFurther questions? Shoot VP Internal, Christine Rankin, a message at christine.rankin@dal.ca . \r\n\r\nMAY THE ODDS BE EVER IN YOUR FAVOUR!', 'Quad Green Space, Dalhousie University', 61),
