('CHAMBER SERIES IV - FLIGHT', 'Concerts, Performances & Arts', '13.00', '2015-03-18', 'Words and music (Marcia Swanston, Susan Stackhouse, Nina Horvath, Shimon Walt) \r\nExploring flights of imagination, nature and the success and failure of Icarus. Works will include excerpts from Antoine de Saint-Exupéry’s The Little Prince, poet Jeffery Beam’s The Life of the Bee set to music by Lee Hoiby, Hahn’s charming Cinq petits chansons, and many other airborne delights.\r\n\r\nCost\r\nPlease call or visit scotiafestival.ns.ca, 902.429.9467\r\nContact\r\n902.429.9467 or visit scotiafestival.ns.ca', 'The Music Room, 6161 Lady Hammond Road', 66),
