('REVOLUTIONS: A DALDANCE RECITAL', 'Concerts, Performances & Arts', '19.00', '2015-03-29', 'DalDance`s annual year-end recital. Hip-hop, jazz, contemporary, ballet, tap, modern, salsa, bellydance and more! The recital is always a great success with a full auditorium- so don`t wait to get your tickets! \r\nDoors will be opening at 6:30pm for a prompt start time at 7pm. The recital is expecting to run until 9pm.\r\n\r\nAdditional Information\r\nTickets are available online, over the phone, or at the ticket booth in the Rebecca Cohn Auditorium.\r\n\r\nCost\r\nGeneral Admission: 10$ Student: 7$\r\nAdditional Information\r\nTickets are available online, over the phone, or at the ticket booth in the Rebecca Cohn Auditorium.\r\n\r\nContact\r\nDaldance Society for any additional information at daldance@dal.ca', 'Rebecca Cohn Auditorium', 92),
