('HALIFAX PLANETARIUM AT DALHOUSIE UNIVERSITY: DOWNTOWN MILKY WAY', 'Training & Professional Development', '07:15 PM', '2015-07-09', 'Admission:  $5 (at the door); reductions for families (min. age 8 years) \r\nReservations required: go to astronomynovascotia.ca\r\nFollow the instructions and specify your show date and time.\r\n\r\nEach show is about an hour long. Full details will be sent before the show. \r\nPlease do not be late; no admission after the door closes.', 'Rm. 120 Dunn Bldg Dalhousie University 6310 Coburg Rd', 150),
