('A SOCIAL WITH STRAWBERRY FLAVOUR', 'On June 26 about 600 of Dals staff and faculty came together on the Studley Quad to enjoy some fresh strawberry shortcake and homemade lemonade.\r\nPresident Richard Florizone kicked off this years event by congratulating staff and faculty for their achievements. He extended his praise to faculty members who won awards in their respective fields.', 'http://www.dal.ca/news/2015/07/03/a-social-with-strawberries.html', '2015-07-03', 'Community & Culture', 118, 'http://www.dal.ca/news/2015/07/03/a-social-with-strawberries/_jcr_content/image.adaptive.579.high.jpg/1435866642647.jpg'),
